{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"black","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1,"bg":"bg_adv_13131.jpg","turnChangeIn":"rollInLogo_PB"},{"autoTurnLast":2.5,"turnChangeOut":"rollOutLogo_Union"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_13141.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-1"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"So, were you able to send Sana's@picture book to Shizuka...?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-2"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Yes, I was able to message it to her..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-3"}],"nameLeft":"Sana","textLeft":"And what did she say...?"},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-4"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Well, not a thing..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-5"}],"nameLeft":"Sana","textLeft":"Could it be that she didn't@even read your message...?"},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-6"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"No, the message was marked as read,@and I confirmed the receipt of the e-book."},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-7"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Since then, however, she hasn't@responded to me at all..."},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-8"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"I tried sending her a few more messages, but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":300,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-9"}],"nameLeft":"Sana","textLeft":"...As a picture book written by an amateur,@it must not have resonated with her..."},{"chara":[{"id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-10"}],"nameLeft":"Sana","textLeft":"It's a very basic story. I'm sorry that@you overestimated me, Sunao..."},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-11"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"No, that isn't the case at all."},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-12"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"I'm sure that if Charu and I were there with her,@she would understand it..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":100401,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-13"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"So, what kind of story is your@picture book about, Sana?"},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-14"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"I've heard you talk about it,@but I haven't read it myself yet..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-15"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"Well, it's sort of embarrassing to talk about..."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-16"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"It's a different story from your@previous book about Ai, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-17"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"That's right..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-18"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Should I just read it, then?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-19"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"D-definitely not!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-20"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"Um, I'd be so embarrassed that I might just die...!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":401,"pos":0,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-21"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"It's that embarrassing?! Then, could I@at least get a summary of it...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100101}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-22","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-21"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"...It's too embarrassing for me to read it myself,@so, Sunao, if you could..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-23"},{"id":100101,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Oh, me...? I don't particularly mind..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":100101}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":102701,"pos":1}],"textClear":1},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102701,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-24"}],"nameCenter":"Sunao","textCenter":"Now then, Miss Futaba's picture book..."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story03","chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-25"}],"nameNarration":"Sunao","narration":"\"Put simply, it is not a story about right and wrong,@but about who is truly suffering,@and who truly needs to be saved.\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-26"}],"narration":"\"The story begins with a turtle,@who is slow at everything and lacks confidence,@meeting a white bird,@who arrives at the village.\""},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-27"}],"narration":"\"From her the turtle learns that,@just by showing kindness befitting her stature,@she can become indispensable to others,@and does what she can little by little.\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-28"}],"narration":"\"But then, a dangerous tiger comes along@and begins stealing food from the village.\""},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-29"}],"narration":"\"The villagers go after the tiger and,@eventually, are able to catch her in a trap.\""},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-30"}],"narration":"\"The tiger asks the turtle for help,@but the turtle, unwilling to aid a scoundrel,@ignores her pleas.\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-31"}],"narration":"\"However, the bird takes action and rescues the tiger,@who apologizes for what she's done@and vows to work for the village from now on.\""},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-32"}],"narration":"\"As the turtle sees this, she realizes that@she had been the one doing wrong here.\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-33"}],"nameCenter":"Sunao","textCenter":"And, that's the story."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102701}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-34"},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"...I thought it was a wonderful story. I'm not@sure why you wanted to hide it from me...?"},{"chara":[{"id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-35"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"Um, that's because..."},{"chara":[{"id":100401,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-36"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"The turtle is me... The tiger is Miss Yuna...@And the bird is you, Iroha..."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-37"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Wha, it was me...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-38"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"Yes..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-39"},{"id":100101,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"Iroha, you said the fighting over@the [textYellow:Kimochi] Stones..."},{"chara":[{"id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-40"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"...ultimately comes from how@we all want to be saved..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-41"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"We have a lot of differences, but in the end,@we're all fighting for the right thing,"},{"chara":[{"id":100401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-42"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"so I think maybe we should reject conflict instead of@each other, and work together to save everyone."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100401,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-43"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"That's why I was hoping I could convey@that with this picture book..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":100101,"motion":301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-44"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"O-oh, I see. I'm happy to hear that. Though..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-45"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"It's a little embarrassing when you@say that right to my face..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":300,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-46"}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"I'm sorry, you must be totally weirded out..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":400,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-47"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Not at all...! I really am happy about it...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-48"},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"For you to write about me like you did for Ai,"},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-49"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"it shows how much you care about my feelings."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":100401,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-50"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"I would similarly be pleased if you chose to draw@a picture book with me as the model."},{"autoTurnLast":2,"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":100,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-51"}],"enableSkipAutoTurn":1,"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"I'm glad that we were able to understand@your feelings, Sana. *Giggle*"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102701}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-52","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-51"}],"enableSkipAutoTurn":0,"nameLeft":"Sana","textLeft":"Yes...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-53"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Now, if only Shizuka could accept@the honest contents of this book..."},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-54"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"She doesn't seem to realize what it is she's doing,"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103002/vo_full_103002-5-55"}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"or who it is that needs to be saved."},{"autoTurnLast":2,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
